boardcam.cutters

Class STLCutter

  • java.lang.Object
    • boardcam.cutters.AbstractCutter
      • boardcam.cutters.STLCutter

  • public class STLCutter
extends AbstractCutter
    This class reads the cutter geometry from an STL-file allowing for general cutters to be designed in an external CAD-program and used in BoardCAD.
